<font color="#FF0000">HANGIN' IN OR HANGIN' OUT?</font><br>
<tt>Thu Apr 24  6:29:39 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
Jay, We all have to deal with &quot;wannabes&quot; in all facets of our lives.  Not just Vietnam.  Look at the guy who can run faster, jump higher, make love longer than anybody else.  The folks who pretend that they were there just have a feeling that they have missed a moment of history.  That is they want to get the accolades that we deserve.<br>
I too, have encountered these folks and I feel pity more than anything else.  The ones who are honest enough to say that they weren't there I simply say &quot;Thank God, that you didn't have to be there.&quot;  Most of these folks immediately shut up if they find out they are in the presence of the real thing.  <br>
So keep on truckin', Bro.  Next week will be 30 years since I got back and I'm goin' to the Wall.<br>
Chet Botkins 1st Cav  3/18th Arty  10/65-5/67<br>

